text: Llynoedd Ieuan is a Site of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion, west Wales, Great Britain. The site is designated as a category IV by the International Union for the Conservation of Nature on the IUCN Protected Area Management Categories scale. ==See also== *List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion ==References== Category:Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion
title: Llynoedd Ieuan
